Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where am I?\N--Oh, you shouldn't move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! The golden belfry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have the duty to protect it to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush, Wyper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vearth, at least, is not refusing anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Right now, at least,\Nno one wants to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's party time!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The long battle of 400 years had ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the citizens of Skypiea continued\Ntheir joyous party day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Made It Here! The Yarn the Poneglyphs Spin"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... I can't drink any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is it?\N--Nami, wake everyone up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna steal the gold and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "idiot"?!\NYou're louder than I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm louder, you say?!\NYou're the louder one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're calling me loud\Nwhen you're really super loud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice is the one that's\Nreally super-mega-ultra loud!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's true!!\NI'm talking loud because you're loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shut up! I can't sleep!!\N--You're the one who spoke loud first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! You're the loud one!!\N--It wasn't me! It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a delicate woman! I wouldn't yell\Nwith my mouth wide open, would I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! There's no way\NI'd do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See? See?! Your mouth is wide open!\N--Geez, wake up, sleepyhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you did hit me here! Here! It's really true!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's because you ticked me off!\N--Nami-san! Good morning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh? It's not morning yet!\N--Yeah, yeah... Go ahead and\Nbe feeble-minded like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Like I said, you don't\Nhave to shout, you know!!\N--What do you mean, "feeble-minded"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Sea people sure like to party, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fourth day in a row.\NTheir vitality isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, guys! It's not often that\Nwe get to visit a sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it so that you'll have no regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! We found the golden bell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's stuck on the fallen Giant Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pulling it out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can help, come to the\Nwestern seashore! Hurry! Hurry up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, guys! Gather everyone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the western seashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The belfry was found!\N--Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--At the western seashore.\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you sure?!\N--Yeah! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they found\Nthe bell that fell in the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Those who can move,\Ngather at the western seashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The belfry was found!\NIt's at the western seashore!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The belfry was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! We still need more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the pride of our ancestors' city,\NShandora. We'll get it at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it everything you got!!\NOne more time!! One, two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull harder!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubber band?! So you call this a rubber band?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! My Usopp Rubber Band did 90%\Nof the work of taking Giant Jack down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa!\N--Whoa! Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one in the world that has them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa!\N--Whoa! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... put that aside for now.\NI'd like to show you this iron sheet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, ladies and gentlemen!\NThis is no ordinary iron sheet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tore it off from the Going Merry,\Nour ship that endured very hard travels
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the Grand Line, as well as Eneru's\Nattacks! It's the "King of Iron Sheets"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?! You guys want iron, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you trade me dials for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I want this rubber band!\NI'll trade you for this rubber band!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I want one, too! Is that okay?!\N--Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa... Are they serious?!\N--Give me one, too!\N--Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water, light, fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things whose shape is transient...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things with no form...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cut them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shells! I got shells! Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lucky, lucky! I got so lucky!\N--You're in a good mood, aren't you, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the negotiation go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that? I got lots of dials!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I press it and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for me! With this many dials,\NI can do many different things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Usopp factory'll be running full steam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro, if you make\Nyour swords Flavor Swords
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and store the smell of\Nstuff like melons in them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can enjoy your everyday training!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No thanks.\N--Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I can make\NNami's Clima Takt stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My slingshot will be incredible, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where are Robin, Luffy and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others are still inside.\NRobin went somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case... this snake's really conked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept dancing day after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...though I don't know\Nwhat he was so happy about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, they'd better come out soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because if he wakes up,\Nhe could give them a hard time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This good-tempered snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! You just don't know\Nhow troublesome he can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This good-tempered snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, you can be so\Noptimistic because you didn't see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what a pain this snake can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This good-tempered snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now listen here, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This good-tempered snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It was a Tone Dial!\N--Don't do stupid stuff like that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's stupid! It's really stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! What does this snake eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we there, yet, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There they are!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty! It looks just like the ones\Nthat we saw at the monkeys' house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? See? See?! There's all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it awesome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How beautiful...\N--Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I didn't expect it to be this...\N--How magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one of the side columns has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but there isn't much we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is... the Poneglyph...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stone that our ancestors\Nrisked the city's life to protect...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is written on it, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something we're better off not knowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hold our true motive in your\Nhearts and speak not of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the ones who weave history...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the sounding of the grand belfry..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were carved on the Shandoran ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were the keepers,\Nentrusted with this for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... You can read those characters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poseidon, the "ancient weapon"\Nnamed after a God...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its whereabouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! What's that?!\N--She said "ancient"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it talking about something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...separate from Pluton\Nthat I read about in Alabasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that one shot from Pluton\Nwill completely destroy an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that there are such dangerous\Nthings in this world waiting to be found...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, this was a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Aren't those the same kind of\Ncharacters on that engraving next to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gol D. Roger"...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it here. I will guide this\Ntext to the ends of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Gol D. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of the Pirates...! Could this mean\Nthat he came to this sky island, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth do these words mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, more importantly,\Nwhy can he use these characters?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it says Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Blue Sea pirate who came\Nto this sky more than 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So his name is engraved there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I don't know how he reached this bell,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this sure is indelible proof that he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, there're two\Nkinds of Poneglyph stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ones with information, and others\Nthat indicate their whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this stone is one of\Nthe ones with information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I made it here. I will guide this\Ntext to the ends of the earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guide this text... Guide...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...!\NCould the Rio Poneglyph be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief... This Poneglyph\Nhas already fulfilled its role!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I bet those Poneglyphs with\Ninformation scattered around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will, when put together, become one text
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that will fill the "Blank History"\Nfor the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the text\Ncompleted by connecting them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Rio Poneglyph,\Nwhich still does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gol D. Roger, King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely delivered this text to its destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Then...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...does that mean that our duty\Nhas been fulfilled as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... don't have to... fight any longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Our ancestors' wish\Nhas been fulfilled, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chief!\N--Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good... Good... So our duty has been fulfilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have to guide the text on those\NPoneglyphs that I read in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the end of the Grand Line... to Raftel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, the feeling that straw hat kid\Ngives me is reminiscent of Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Monkey D. Luffy.\NMy interest in him never fades.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D? I see. He's got the same letter in his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... and I'm sure it's a big issue\Nthat has something to do with history.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, young lady...\NYou guys wanted gold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it's more valuable\Nthan Vearth in the Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about taking the broken belfry column,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though we can't give you the bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, we have to show our\Nappreciation to you guys somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right!\N--Don't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?! They'll be happy to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then! Let's bring\Nthis to the Blue Sea people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrap it with cloths! It's hard to carry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give this to those who saved our land!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this thing's huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Robin doing? She's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this place is\Nso empty. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did the\Nguerrillas and angels go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's better they aren't here.\NIf they find us, they'll chase us around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're trying to steal this much\Ngold and run, they won't just let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Nami and Conis are preparing\Nto set sail, but we still have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, Sanji, do you\Nhave something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not until we get to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've gotta have\Nsomething to munch on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give me some!\N--What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We don't have to wait for that woman, do we?\N--I can't give you what I\Ndon't have! Just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go on ahead and get on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Idiot! Don't!\N--Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Idiot Moss Head!\N--Moss Head Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go into the forest alone, you won't\Nmake it three steps without getting lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! It's Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo, Robin!! Hurry! Hurry up!\NWe've gotta run!! We stole some gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Don't say that!\NTake a good look behind her!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all coming back here together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's tons of them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! This is bad! This is super bad!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's that? A huge cannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's gotta be it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all came back all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the ship! We can no longer stay here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check this out! We got a good catch!\NThe bag's stuffed! We're rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? They all have bags on their back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... Are they already leaving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop, you guys!! Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Stop! Stop, you guys!\N--See?! They found us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll strike a pose and say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys say, "Stop! Stop!" but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Tell them, Usopp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We risked our lives to come\Nall the way to this sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right!\N--And we've found the legendary city of gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin-chan! Hurry up! We'll be caught!\N--How the heck can we, proud pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just go back empty-handed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Caught?! What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we want to do is thank them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Miss, aren't you guys\Ngonna take this gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Run!!\N--Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all after us! It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that?! Wasn't I cool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan! Hurry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Keep running all the\Nway to the end of the sky!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling lonely, talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gaze at the heavens\Nas you wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the moon,\Nyou keep your gaze constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your deep reflection wanes\Nas you slowly disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are, let those words guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream, you travelers who spend\Ncountless nights drifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you may not be able to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely start moving forward again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, everyone! We'll split the treasure\Nonce we get back down, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep it safe, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where?!\N--It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'll tell you where\NI hide my secret stash, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.56,0:23:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie! Her eyes say she's telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.73,0:23:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, guys! We're going back to the Blue Sea!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.40,0:23:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Off to the Blue Sea!! Finale Woven by Feelings"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
